  "description": [
    "Saturday pet 15 937 TERRORISM OR LAW 5 vr 1 V Cautiously so as not to frighten the timid our daily papers inform us that the strike of theatrical employes has necessitated the calling out of every available police officer to guard the theaters Several amusement houses have been bombed others have had their audiences sprayed with vile fluids and by whom The ruffian element that has wormed its way into the labor movementthe fa natical halfbaked element the lawless minority that ever seeks to rule by terror where it can never hope to rule by number And this terroristic element has reason to feel its safety in the present strike It has seen gunmen boldly stalk the streets of this city in search of their prey It has seen gunmen shoot down men in cold blood and go unscathed It has seen thugs and gangsters roam the city unmolested and it has seen their known haunts go unraid ed by tihe police It has seen more than that It has sesn known gangsters walk brazen ly into the office of our Chief of Police and jauntily walk out againsmiling It has seen or read the ac counts of gangsters"
  ],
